{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC08_LOG_100.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x14,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Ah, Sophie. There's something I wanted to ask you... Why are you using alchemy?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2a,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "W-why the sudden question?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x2c,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Well... I was just curious. You don't see many people using this power. Why did you start using it?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Hmm... At first, I was just copying what my grandma did."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2c,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "But when I started working with it, and helping other people using alchemy, it started becoming more and more fun..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2c,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Lately, I've been wanting to make lots of people happy using alchemy..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x2d,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "That's a really straightforward reason..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2d,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "Huh? It is?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Yeah, I think it's admirable."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x4a,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "O-oh stop, you're embarrassing me."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x4c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "By the way, why did you decide to become a blacksmith, Logy?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Me? My dad was a blacksmith, so that's my reason. It's pretty simple."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "I see..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "But I actually want to make weapons so that people can travel."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "So that people can travel?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x3e,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "Yeah. I traveled to all kinds of places, saw beautiful scenery, and met great people."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "But many of the roads were dangerous."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "If I make weapons that are easy to handle, people who aren't very strong would be much safer while traveling."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "My goal is to make weapons that allow people to travel wherever they want, with peace of mind."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2c,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "(Logy's dream is really wonderful...)"
        }
    ]
}